text: Arantza Gumucio (born 4 October 1989) is a Chilean competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 49erFX. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Chile Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 49erFX
